headline: 2 Dirt Cheap Stocks to Buy With $200 Right Now
summary: Shares of Carnival are rising as the cruise line pays off its debt, but the stock still remains very cheap.  Williams-Sonoma shares are starting to climb as it demonstrates resilience in a tough environment.  Consider Carnival (NYSE: CCL) (NYSE: CUK) and Williams-Sonoma (NYSE: WSM), which are trading at dirt cheap prices despite running excellent businesses and having a long growth runway.
